    <tr>
      <td colspan="13">
          <span style="color:red;">*</span> The listed companies or their directors or executives have any scandalous corporate governance issues such as regulatory wrong-doings, bribery, and corruption. In this case, the CGR information should be used with care and in conjunction with the related governance news.&nbsp;
      </td>
    </tr>
    
    
  </table>
  </td>
